      "writtenOn": "2021-04-06T18:57:13Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "nit: seems like this variable is needed only to do Stat(). Consider using it only there, while the rest of code (L66, L71) uses less-specific `body`.\n\nIt would also make L68-71 easier to read: it calls Seek() on one variable, but then uses another.\n\n--\n\nbut stepping back, it would be simpler if this code was less conditional. Did you consider a simple rule that if someone passes content in t.art.Content, then use Batch upload? The client shouldn\u0027t pass content there if the artifact is large; and if it isn\u0027t large, then we should use Batch.\n\nMaybe not in this CL since we don\u0027t have batch upload yet.",
      "range": {
